{
  "stem": "4570.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now they were stuck with 1,000 women, and they didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think that they gave us long johns.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really know-- I must try how to find out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I really have the feeling that a thousand women-- and the moon was shining and we went across this drawbridge.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it must have looked so, so ridiculous, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So eventually, we went further, further into a building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mauthausen is enormous.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not as big as Auschwitz, but very big.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we came to the barrack and it had typhoid written on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "God, what now?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, the same.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The same thing, that the-- you know, the beds above each other and so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I don't know how long I was there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three weeks, two weeks, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next to us was a camp, and the men were like skeletons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they came all running out, looking us over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was this one poor fellow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was totally naked, had a bandaged penis and a belt around his waist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the belt he had a spoon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he wasn't Czech or German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he started talking to me, [LAUGHS] and I didn't-- I didn't want anything to do with him, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then there were some Czech people there, also prisoners, not Jews, in the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow they came also with messages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I don't know what jobs they had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They could move freely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they came to, to welcome us, like the Czech girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we got a little bit of feedback that, that things are-- unless the gas comes, that things are not so bad, that Americans are coming closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
